      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <span class="highlight"><%= user.name %></span>,</p>
        <p>Your payment was successfully processed. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="details">
          <p>
            <span class="emoji">ðŸ’°</span> <strong>Amount:</strong>
            <span class="highlight">â‚¹<%= amount %></span>
