        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best Regards,<br />The PlanItNow Team</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: #64748b">
          This is an automated message - please do not reply directly
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
